data.title: Woodburn Medical Park
data.meta_description: Woodburn Medical Park is a 174,000 SF medical office park with over 40 synergistic medical and dental practices in Fairfax County. The two-buildings make up a medical park in a bustling area.
data.text:
Spotlight: 3289 & 3299 Woodburn Road, Annandale, VA 22003

Woodburn Medical Park is a 174,000 SF medical office park with over 40 synergistic medical and dental practices in Fairfax County. The two buildings make up an expansive medical park in a bustling area and are across the street from leading-edge care. These buildings were recently renovated, including newly painted exteriors, new exterior entrances, common areas, and restrooms.

Location: Fairfax County

Woodburn Medical Park is located in the hub of Fairfax County. Directly off of the Capital Beltway, it’s easily accessible from Annandale and Falls Church. Woodburn Medical Park also has easy access from Route 50 and Gallows Road. Fairfax County is located 15 miles outside of DC, and neighbors Alexandria and Arlington.

The Woodburn neighborhood of Fairfax County is home to about 8,462 individuals, with a median age of 39. The average household income is $130,448 and 85% of individuals have white-collar jobs.

Neighbor: Inova Fairfax Medical Campus

This medical park is steps away from the nationally recognized Inova Fairfax Hospital. Inova’s flagship location, it’s the largest hospital campus in Northern Virginia, with 923 beds. The Inova Fairfax Medical Campus includes the Inova Fairfax Hospital, Inova Heart and Vascular Institute, Inova Schar Cancer Institute, Inova Neurosciences Institute, Inova Children’s Hospital, and Inova Women’s Hospital. The campus is also home to Northern Virginia’s only Level 1 Trauma Center and offers organ transplant programs for hearts, lungs, kidneys, and pancreases.

On-site Amenities

Woodburn Medical Park offers many on-site amenities to both tenants and patients.

The amenities include:

On-site radiology

Surgery center

Laboratory testing services

On-site deli

On-site bank, and a

Recently upgraded common area

Gurney size elevators

Electronic directories

Operable windows

The medical park also has abundant garage and surface parking with direct access from the parking garage to multiple floors.

Medical Office Availability

The Class B office buildings feature a total of 180,324 SF. There are 16 office spaces available for lease at 3289 and 3299 Woodburn Road, Annandale, VA, 22003, totaling 47,631 SF.

The Fast Facts:

1,200-9,500 SF suites available

200 parking spaces available (4/1,000 SF Ratio)

Within walking distance of Inova hospital
